                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra in Text I-4 (Māryām); titles and
                           numbers of the Psalms, Canticles and Songs; title of Texts I-2, I-3;
                           title and incipit of the daily readings of Text I-4; name and number of
                           the Hebrew letters in Ps. 118; stichometry; refrains of Texts I-4 and I-5
                           and their abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs and text
                           dividers; Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
